.section
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-6.offset-md-3
      .text-center
        = image_tag 'black-and-white.png', id: 'black-and-white', class: 'circle-image'
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
      %h1
        About me
.section.about-me-summary
  .row.mb-5
    .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
      %h3
        TLDR
      %p
        A Florida native currently residing in Los Angeles, California, my name is
        Alexander Smith (Alex). While I call Tampa home, I was born in
        Baltimore, MD and I've been to Germany more times than my fingers
        permit me to count. I have a black belt in Taekwondo (it's been awhile
        though). I originally planned to join the military and was in ROTC in
        High School. My friends call me an adrenaline junkie because I love
        anything with an engine. I've had experience with 4-wheelers, go-karts,
        boats, jet skis, motorcycles, sports cars, and more. If it goes fast,
        I'm interested. Speaking of interested, want to learn more?  You can
        read more about...
      %p
        %a{ href: '#past' } How I went from flipping burgers at the neighborhood DQ to Wall Street.
      %p
        %a{ href: '#present' } How I retired from being a corporate mercenary and became a Full-Stack Developer at a startup.
      %p
        %a{ href: '#future' } What I'm working towards next.
      %p
        %a{ href: '/blog' } Things I've written.
      %p
        And while we're still talking about me, you can
        %a{ href: '/' } hire me
        to help
        = succeed '!' do
          %span{ style: 'font-style: italic;' } you
        = partial 'partials/contact_me_btn'
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
      %h3
        Quick timeline of professional experience
      %p
        Clicking on the company titles will take you to the section of my story
        describing the position. You can also check out my resume
        = succeed "." do
          %a{ href: '/alex_smith_resume.pdf', target: '_blank' } here
        = partial 'partials/experience_links'
.row
  .col
    %hr
.section#past
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
      %h3
        Where I've been
      %p.about-me-quote
        %i.fa.fa-quote-left.fa-3x.fa-pull-left
        You don't know where you're going until you know where you've been.
      %br
      %p.about-me-text
        = partial 'partials/past'
.row
  .col
    %hr
.section#present
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
      %h3
        Where I am
      %p.about-me-quote
        %i.fa.fa-quote-left.fa-3x.fa-pull-left
        Our DNA is 96% chimpanzee. Is that even worth arguing?! If I gave
        you a sandwich that was filled with 96% sh*t and 4% ham, would you
        be willing to consider that a ham sandwich? So If you ever start
        taking things too seriously, just remember that we are talking monkeys
        on an organic spaceship flying through the universe. - Joe Rogan
      %br
      %p.about-me-text
        = partial 'partials/present'
.row
  .col
    %hr
.section#future
  .row
    .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
      %h3
        Where I'm going
      %p.about-me-quote
        %i.fa.fa-quote-left.fa-3x.fa-pull-left
        I don't regret the things I've done, only the things I've never tried.
      %br
      %p
        = partial 'partials/future'
.row
  .col
    %hr
