      %h3
        Hobbies and interests
      %p
        Hobbies and interests can be so vague...I like to think of this section
        as answers to the question of, "what are some things that you would go
        out of your way to do in your free time?". But that's not a cool title
        so I still call these hobbies and interests.
      %p
